distraction: I was not doing anything else. I fully concentrating on the task as in required my full attention.
strategies: I was just mastering the paired objects. This was easier since some of the objects appeared more frequent than the other. Also i was trying to form a story in my mind with the paired objects so it became easier to recall.
easier: Yes some were easier to learn. Some were so easy for for a story from the pairs. For instance a painting and a wheelchair. I came up with a story of using the paints to pain the wheelchair
comments: The task was enjoyable as it required one to be fully attantive. Hence one can not easily be distracted. I love it. Am looking forward to more studies of the sort in the near future. Thank you
